<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1787149-is-there-an-index-of-characters-and">Is there an index of characters and places? I bought the audible version and I&#39;m having trouble keeping the names straight.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1787149'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F304217.Viriconium">like</a></span>

